; carta prodotta con la stessa; scritto; libro.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"47px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:47px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><em>(dall\'Italiano contemporaneo)</em> :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"24px\"}}} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>collettività di appassionati del libro.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:cover -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"211px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:211px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"className\":\"o-typing-delay-500ms\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center o-typing-delay-500ms\"><o-anim-typing><strong>BYBLOS</strong> FA PER TE SE</o-anim-typing>:</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"94px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:94px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":569,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/biblos/home/pexels-pixabay-433333-3/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":29} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:29% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/biblos/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/pexels-pixabay-433333-3-683x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-569 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Contenuto…\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Sei un lettore accanito senza più spazio in casa.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">La lista dei tuoi libri da leggere cresce, ma hai un budget limitato.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Hai trovato degli scatoloni pieni zeppi di libri e non sai cosa fartene.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Sei una piccola libreria del territorio che desidera accrescere il proprio raggio di azione.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Cerchi ispirazione!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":\"115px\"} -->\n<div style=\"height:115px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"ast-global-color-6\",\"textColor\":\"ast-global-color-7\",\"width\":25,\"style\":{\"border\":{\"radius\":\"21px\"},\"elements\":{\"link\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"var:preset|color|ast-global-color-7\"}}},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"16px\"}},\"className\":\"o-anim-hover is-style-fill\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-25 has-custom-font-size o-anim-hover is-style-fill\" style=\"font-size:16px\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-ast-global-color-7-color has-ast-global-color-6-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-text-align-center wp-element-button\" href=\"https://localhost/biblos/registrazione/\" style=\"border-radius:21px\"><strong>Registrati</strong></a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" cla